# Scanner agents

## File layout

- `packages/agents/{vuln,config,infra,supply,specialized}/{name}.scanner.ts`
- Colocated `{name}.scanner.test.ts`

## Scanner contract

```typescript
export const myScanner: Scanner = {
  meta: {
    id: 'config.missing-hsts',  // must match scanner-catalog.md
    name: 'Missing HSTS',
    category: 'configuration',
    description: '...',
    tags: ['headers', 'tls'],
    estimatedMs: 500,
    requiresUrl: true,
  },
  async run(ctx) {
    if (!ctx.target.url) return [];
    // ... return Finding[] or []
  },
};
```

## Finding rules

- Use `buildAiFixPrompt()` from `core` — never omit `aiFixPrompt`
- Return `[]` when target type does not apply; throw only on unexpected errors
- Single-purpose scanners; no multi-check mega-files

## Testing

Mock `ScannerContext`; assert severity, `id`, and redacted evidence.
